{"tid":1032940,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"諗緊走唔走堂嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-02-22T17:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T13:23:26.000Z","uid":74530,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae04e6511244fe0725aeae7626a7179c7594066f","tid":1032940,"uid":74530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:52:04.000Z","msg":"從經濟學嘅角度睇<br />\n走堂 / 唔走堂純粹係上堂價值同機會成本之間嘅取捨<br />\n如果上堂價值係10，番part time價值係8，你係應該揀上堂<br />\n但如果上堂價值係5，理性嘅人係應該揀番part time<br />\n無論如何，<br />\n走堂同唔走堂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">都同大學學費完全無關</span></span></strong><br />\n因為依個係「沉沒成本」(Sunk cost)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學學費係固定$42,100嘅<br />\n不論你上抑或唔上都係焗比<br />\n唔會因為你上一堂佢就嘔番$400比你<br />\n(嗰d咩「走一堂損失四百元」可以坐番低先)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更何況其實大家心裡面都好清楚<br />\n$168,400支付嘅係張cert<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而唔係上堂費<br />\n屌你如果我話你錢照比堂照上但我唔比張cert你你估你制唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n$68,000都唔撚制啦下話？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上堂嘅目的係咩？<br />\n為咗見個Professor？貪佢靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然係為咗學習知識<br />\n以前資訊封閉，好多知識都要係圖書館搵<br />\n最快同準確咁獲取正確知識嘅方法就會係問教授<br />\n因為佢同你講解嘅時間成本比你從圖書館亂搵低<br />\n所以你上堂嘅效率係最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但依家我地係活係資訊氾濫嘅世代<br />\n係Google/YouTube學習遠比留係lecture hall聽教授讀ppt嚟得有效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係我洗幾十US係Coursera/Udemy買個課程<br />\n入面嘅material根本屌打大學成個course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得如果你真係要上堂得幾個原因<br />\n教授好撚靚仔/女 (番去睇av啦屌)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAttendance計course分(要用到依招夾春袋逼學生上堂真係唔好學人教書)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做lab(無野好講，聽日準時番學啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你問心真係學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: CS major，gpa3.6"},{"pid":"bdd99d5601a13a3fd690f8e20543b3a587c7c261","tid":1032940,"uid":226413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T17:59:50.000Z","msg":"明白"},{"pid":"17d48bd7eb9b5cae3bb13a44be41dea361ee0ffb","tid":1032940,"uid":161063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"it應該係最易上網自學嘅科，其他科我就唔知喇"},{"pid":"778c6a642a1ed182cc59c37c7623c6f4dde43ede","tid":1032940,"uid":128111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:16:27.000Z","msg":"Lecture 不嬲垃圾咖啦，得個聽字吸收得幾多"},{"pid":"fb9684bc04b18d5974444d86b1d3f35a5011dd37","tid":1032940,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"有啲教授嘅堂真係值得上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好享受"},{"pid":"bd5b2354588db3ff649d8b45d95f1be1247a4510","tid":1032940,"uid":237240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:46:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"411c24a02804f5c0ce31abb83412bcfea8b16a74","tid":1032940,"uid":132326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"3.6好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3799864c90337501f4e750fd657ff503530c344","tid":1032940,"uid":74530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17d48bd7eb9b5cae3bb13a44be41dea361ee0ffb","tid":1032940,"uid":161063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"it應該係最易上網自學嘅科，其他科我就唔知喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"的確藝術/演藝嗰d科目又真係要上堂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通自己上網搵個裸體model學人體素描咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd3c925968bd544b5f634e9adf50bc579bde927","tid":1032940,"uid":74530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"411c24a02804f5c0ce31abb83412bcfea8b16a74","tid":1032940,"uid":132326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"3.6好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"明白天外有天人外有人<br />\n比我好成績嘅人多的是<br />\n但我想指出嘅係<br />\n成績好壞係視乎學得到唔到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係上唔上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007189db645faffa0a108960e3423f4c91588069","tid":1032940,"uid":74530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"如果屋企人問起做咩成日唔上堂<br />\n你可以理直氣壯咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學習係目的(ends)<br />\n上堂係手段(means)<br />\n當我搵到個更有效率嘅手段去完成目的<br />\n唔可能再去行回頭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11da23f7fd93391473add6024d86350e28fdffd","tid":1032940,"uid":4739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"對考試而言上堂聽貼士有效過自己鳩溫"}]}